msgid_plural "plutonium laser charges"
msgstr[0] "钚激光充能弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'plutonium laser charge'}
#: .\nm_ammo.json
msgid ""
"Prepared handmade laser charge, made from plutonium cell. Isn't supposed to "
"work at all, but for some reason does. Deals large amount of damage."
msgstr "预制手工激光充能弹，由钚电池制成。本不应工作，但不知为何可行。造成大量伤害。"

