#. ~ Description for {'str': 'plutonium heavy laser charge'}
#: .\nm_ammo.json
msgid ""
"Prepared handmade plutonium laser charge, designed for use in heavy laser. "
"An entire power of a plutonium cell, concentrated in a single pack, it's "
"obviously an overkill for anything less than a tank."
msgstr "预制手工钚激光充能弹，专为重型激光武器设计。将钚电池的全部能量集中在一个弹包中，显然对坦克以下的任何目标都是过度杀伤。"

#: .\nm_ammo.json
