#. ~ Description for {'str': 'NM1001 watch'}
#: .\nm_armor.json
msgid ""
"A small device developed by Nimian Manufacture. When fixed near the eye, "
"accurately shows time and temperature, and can provide more information on "
"the weather upon activation."
msgstr "尼米安制造公司开发的小型设备。固定在眼睛附近时，能准确显示时间和温度，激活后还可提供更多天气信息。"

